plot: Gon is overwhelmed by Genthru's power, but he isn't backing down.

With two of the members of Team Genthru down, Gon is left in a standoff with just Genthru himself. Everything Gon and his team had planned were coming together. Selfishly though, Gon decides to temporarily ignore the plan because he wanted to try something out, getting badly damaged in the process. Gon finally pulls through as Team Genthru is defeated. With the most dangerous team all tied up and Gon now having collected all 99 reserved card slots, a special game event is due to take place in order to receive the #00 card. But before all that... Gon and his team need to decide how they should use "Breath of Archangel" and whether to use it on themselves or Bomber and his team mates.—paulp1988
